275
00:18:15,416 --> 00:18:17,250
[HIMEKO]
I hate that delinquent.

276
00:18:17,333 --> 00:18:19,166
[MARUTA]
You mean Yuzu Aihara?

277
00:18:19,250 --> 00:18:22,875
