289
00:19:21,291 --> 00:19:23,125
[YUZU]
Sorry, Harumin.

290
00:19:23,208 --> 00:19:26,500
Uh, I forgot that I have plans,
but we can text later!

291
00:19:28,083 --> 00:19:31,333
