293
00:19:36,416 --> 00:19:39,541
Hey, slow down!
No running in the halls!

294
00:19:41,958 --> 00:19:43,375
That was her.

295
00:19:49,291 --> 00:19:51,250
Uh, hey!

296
00:19:51,333 --> 00:19:53,958
