297
00:19:54,041 --> 00:19:58,583
Uh, sorry. And I'm sorry
about yesterday too!

298
00:19:58,666 --> 00:20:01,916
I shouldn't have let my
temper get the best of me.

299
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:05,041
[MEI] I didn't call you here
to make you apologize.

300
00:20:06,750 --> 00:20:08,083
So...?

301
00:20:08,166 --> 00:20:11,875
[MEI] This book, it was found
amongst your belongings.

302
00:20:14,666 --> 00:20:18,166
[YUZU]
The manga I bought yesterday!

303
00:20:18,250 --> 00:20:19,833
I thought it was in my bag.

304
00:20:19,916 --> 00:20:22,541
