I don't get this!

314
00:21:11,750 --> 00:21:13,625
[YUZU]
Since that kiss,

315
00:21:13,708 --> 00:21:16,958
Mei is the only thing
I can ever think about.

316
00:21:20,291 --> 00:21:22,625
[YUZU]
There's no going back now.

317
00:21:24,416 --> 00:21:27,166
I'm sorry I'm such a bad sister.

318
00:23:32,291 --> 00:23:34,125
Look, I've been the
president's closest friend

319
00:23:34,208 --> 00:23:35,708
